These tests exercise the features of falco

test.sh runns all the tests.

Each test demonstrates features of falco:
Makefile - how to use falco in a makefile, this is a build example
build - test the different positive and ngative outcomes
database - test for the existance of the database 
help - make sure the help works
items - test the -i items feature
packagename - the packagename has some subtlties that are demonstrated 
test.sh - the test harness for all thse tests
testlist.txt - an example of how to use a list of package and versions 
version - test the version logic in falco
workfile - test the workfile logic 


